vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for and an ordinance granting a Planned Development District for IR Industrial Research District uses and multifamily use on property zoned an IR Industrial Research District, on the south side of Southwell Road, west of Ables Lane, adjacent to the North Stemmons Freeway right-of-way
Recommendation of Staff:  Denial 
Recommendation of CPC:  Approval, subject to a development plan and conditions
Z190-204(ND)
